{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3672f159d1","title":"周恩来对科学院哲学社会科学部两次谈话中有关清查“五·一六”的内容","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1538fcc69a","index":0,"year":1969,"month":6,"day":28,"articleId":"3672f159d1"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"3766d87da7","name":"革命大批判","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"75e62558d2","name":"清理阶级队伍","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"cea9ce86b7","name":"清查五·一六","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"7a99cebe4e","name":"周恩来"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"9067136eaf","type":"title","text":"周恩来对科学院哲学社会科学部两次谈话中有关清查“五·一六”的内容","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3672f159d1"},{"id":"c365f6f3d1","type":"authors","text":"周恩来","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3672f159d1"},{"id":"97c752b2f4","type":"subtitle","text":"6月28日和7月31日两次讲话摘录：","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3672f159d1"},{"id":"f885dbdbad","type":"paragraph","text":"“五·一六”是利用1967年发表《5.16通知》搞起来的，他们抓的很快，主席抓的更快。姚文元9月份发表文章点“五·一六”是反动组织，主席8月份就抓住了，主席看的准……“五·一六”串连，小报上都透露了，主席很快就发现了，矛头不对。原来后台就是王、关、戚。起头，我们想分化他们，把戚本禹分出来，实际上他们是一伙。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3672f159d1"},{"id":"fdb8edd017","type":"paragraph","text":" （1969年6月28日接见学部宣传队和大联委时的讲话）","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3672f159d1"},{"id":"fdfc0b7a8d","type":"paragraph","text":"要先从提高思想、落实政策方面入手。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3672f159d1"},{"id":"1526793669","type":"paragraph","text":"你们要把“五·一六”、大批判、清队、整党搞好。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3672f159d1"},{"id":"bdc8d11c92","type":"paragraph","text":" （1969年7月31日接见学部宣传队和大联委时的讲话）","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3672f159d1"}],"page":{"id":"d02d420934","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3672f159d1","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}